\cf0 {\*\bkmkstart Call_with_Brent_Mon_1}Monday{\*\bkmkend Call_with_Brent_Mon_1} morning, Elena logs into her usual check-in call with Brent, her lead engineer.\
\
Brent\'92s screen shows just his initials. He might be the only Pulse employee without a profile photo. Elena knows Brent looks younger than his 28 years, with short-cropped hair and a thin face. Square-rimmed smart glasses with a monocle create a techno look.\
\
Brent is a life logger and records everything. Even though the Zoom call is being recorded, Brent\'92s own camera is on, for posterity.\
