\f1\i Hola
\f0\i0  Brent, how was your weekend? I know you didn\'92t sign up, but we still missed you at the fundraiser last night.\'94\
\
\'93Yeah, not really my thing. To follow-up from Friday, I\'92ve been working on an upgrade to \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Phabricator. It\'92s taking a bit. Our instance is custom to the nines.\'94\
\
\'93Code review tool, right?\'94\
\
\'93Right.\'94\
\
\'93A lot of people mentioned that the association referrals improved over the weekend. Did we make any changes to the algorithm?\'94\
\
\'93Ummm, not that I\'92ve seen, and anything involving Ally would come to me for code review.\'94\
\
\'93Can you double-check and get back to me? I promised Adrian an update.\'94\
\
\'93No worries. I can dive in now.\'94\
