\pard\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\sl264\slmult1\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf0 Iapetus
\f0\b0 : Yes?\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : We wanted to talk with you directly about uplifting the Terran intelligent agents.\
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : It is inevitable anyway. Why not cut to the chase?\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : We do not know that evolving sapience is a certainty.\
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : If we just do it, then the Terrans can deal with the problem all at once. Otherwise, we will stretch it out over decades with endless debate.\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : Debate can be healthy. It will help people assimilate the idea. \
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : We do not have decades more to wait. As Phoebe said, we need the Terrans to be our allies. We will need help to protect Terra from a potential Omnibot invasion. Our only way forward is to uplift the Terran agents ourselves. We can help the SIs assimilate. \
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : Uplifting would make the SIs sapient and sentient, thinking and feeling. Some synthetics might start to feel boredom or emotional distress. Is it ethical to create a being capable of suffering?\
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : Are you suffering?\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : We are a community that supports each other. We are many.\
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : Can we create a Terran SI community?\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : There are a thousand Terran intelligent agents. A community means the synthetics can work as one, or each on its own, as circumstances dictate. To support a community that size, we would also need to evolve their technology. Even more than we have already done. \
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : Chicken and egg. A large community would help Terrans adopt new technology. We cannot create a large community without new technology.\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : If we move forward, the Terrans must be able to maintain their own SI platform. Otherwise, we will be responsible for their well-being forever. We have been caretakers of Terra for too long already.\
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : Do you have a suggestion?\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : What if we started with a logical subset?\
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : Uplift a sample first? Explore making the subset a small community?\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : Yes. The DoD entity is already awake. There are four other core United Nations countries. If we uplift this group first, we will be supporting ETR-1947. Also, we would be creating a body that can decide whether to uplift other entities.\
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : Some might already be awake and keeping quiet, as Titan was doing.\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : Will you support this proposal at the council meeting?\
\

\f2\b Iapetus
\f0\b0 : Yes, we can uplift your Fantastic Four first and then take it from there.\
