Marquez turns to face the Titan analysts. \'93Dr. Hammond and Dr. Caprica, I know the upgrade is news to you. I wanted everyone to find out at once. After this meeting, you should start training Titan as a dual system. \'97 We\'92ll talk more later.\'94\
