\'93We will not get a better chance to acquire a working Omnibot,\'94 says the Idisi.\
\
\'93We do not have time for a debate. Bring it,\'94 says Oceanus.\
\
\'93Selene,\'94 says Oceanus, \'93close the crate and adjust the other crates in the truck so that it does not look like one is missing. Return the keys, then exfil as quickly as possible.\'94\
\
