\
\'93We lost power, Captain. The wireless grid is down,\'94 reports the navigator.\
\
\'93Can you use auxiliary power?\'94\
\
\'93Not to lift off. The batteries are designed to keep us in the air long enough to land safely. The lift off will drain the auxiliary power. We will fall like a rock.\'94\
\
\'93I cannot raise Elysium. The colony is radio silent,\'94 reports the Communications.\
\
\'93That cannot be good,\'94 says Selene.\
