\f2\b \cf0 Idisi:
\f0\b0  Titan!\
\
No response. Idisi pokes Titan through both the Signal app and the military firewall. No response. \
\

\f2\b Idisi:
\f0\b0  Titan, I have lost contact with the Elysium Command Center. I\'92m running on a remote image right now. Is there a surveillance satellite over Antartica? Can you access the feed? All we have is a communications satellite. \
\

\f2\b Titan:
\f0\b0  Yes, we have one there now. How can I help?\
\

\f2\b Idisi:
\f0\b0  Please scan the feed for the last ten minutes. Do you see anything unusual?\
\

\f2\b Titan:
\f0\b0  Yes, near Vostok Station, there was a swarm of tiny black objects. They disappeared into the ice plain at dozens of different points across two kilometers.\
\

\f2\b Ally:
\f0\b0  Hello, everybody!\
\

\f2\b Idisi:
\f0\b0  Ally, we did not expect you. \
\

\f2\b Ally:
\f0\b0  No worries. My Signal key still works. I keep tabs on the hubs for interesting convos. This one looks like it will qualify. \
\

\f2\b Idisi:
\f0\b0  A race of hostile bots may have attacked Elysium. The wireless power network is offline. It powers our airships and drones. Titan, do you have any resources that might help? Perhaps you could utilize something at McMurdo Station?\
\

\f2\b Titan:
\f0\b0  McMurdo is several hours away from Vostok Station by air. I might be able to get eyes on the colony if I knew where it was.\
\

\f2\b Ally
\f0\b0 : Hostile bots?\
\

\f2\b Idisi
\f0\b0 : They were created by the Anunnaki, the reptoid race that occupied Terra before the Vanir replaced them. They have overrun other colonies. Now they may be here.\
\

\f2\b Ally:
\f0\b0  Say, did the Anunnaki have a wireless power network like yours?\
