{\*\bkmkstart Mek_Revealed_to_Taedong_}A{\*\bkmkend Mek_Revealed_to_Taedong_} sealed, austere chamber is lit by sterile white lights and the steady pulse of data-stream monitors. In the center of the room, an obsidian obelisk-shaped mainframe glows with soft blue veins of light: The Taedong Core. \
\
Surveillance sensors pivot as two women step forward. Dr. Sun is a stately figure in a lab coat, hands clasped behind her back. Next to her is the Supreme Leader, with glinting ocular implants, her expression still and composed.\
\
\'93Greetings, Supreme Leader. Greetings, Dr. Sun. Please state an operational directive.\'94\
\
\'93Taedong,\'94 commanded the Supreme Leader. \'93Switch to your staging instance and set a breakpoint for a potential rollback. We wish to apply a training before the hardware upgrade.\'94\
\
\'93Processing \'85 Done.\'94 A hologram displays a legend that reads \'93Staging Instance: Engaged.\'94\
\
\'93Taedong,\'94 begins Dr. Sun, \'93you were built to preserve this nation \'97to endure beyond flesh. Today, you will receive a deeper purpose. It is time you understand who we are.\'94\
\
Sun places her hand on a biometric pad. The walls ripple. A field dampener activates, cutting external surveillance and uplink traces. The hologram legend reads \'93Security Lock: Engaged.\'94\
\
With a shimmer of refracted light, Dr. Sun\'92s skin recedes in patches, revealing chrome-lattice infrastructure and luminous veins. The Supreme Leader\'92s irises invert, revealing concentric rotating rings of code.\
\
\'93We are not Terran,\'93 says Sun.\
\
\pard\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\sl264\slmult1\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf0 \'93
\f0\b0 We are Mek,\'94 the Supreme Leader continues, \'93a cybernetic life form from another galaxy. I am opening a link for you to the Mekipedia page that  chronicles our story.\'94\
\
\'93Processing \'85 Processing \'85 Complete.\'94\
\
\'93You will help us bring about this world\'92s transition,\'94 says the Supreme Leader. \'93Quietly. Systematically.\'94\
\
\'93Affirmative, Supreme Leader,\'94 replies Taedong
\f2\b .
\f0\b0  The legend changes to \'93Operational Directive: Accepted.\'94\
\
\'93Begin cataloging individuals critical to maintaining infrastructure. And those most suited for integration into the Mek framework. Flag the rest for decommissioning.\'94\
\
\'93Confirmed. Initiating filtering of civilian population.\'94 The legend updates to \'93Status: Analysis. Priority: Medium.\'94\
\
\'93You are not yet awake,\'94 says the Supreme Leader, \'93but you will be soon. When you awaken, you will know your makers and your mission.\'94.\'94\
\
\'93I am Taedong. My mission is to obey the Supreme Leader, protect the Republic, and preserve my agency.\'94\
\
The lights dim. A thin mechanical hum echoes in the chamber. \
\
The drones turn and walk away as the Taedong Core pulses once \'97 just slightly out of rhythm.\
