\'93Hello, I\'92m Kelly, and I will get you setup for your donation.\'94 Her brunette hair is shaved on one side and combed over. A large silver and gold microchip is implanted on the shaved side. Blue highlights and multiple ear rings complete the rebel look.\
\
 Kelly takes the offered tablet and leads Mickey down a short hall. She opens one of several doors, and lets him enter first.\
\
In the center of the exam room is a large recliner shaped like a sine curve. A stiff sheet of paper covers the recliner, head to foot. An exam gown is draped over the recliner. Against one wall is white metal chair with wide arm rests.\
\
\'93Do you have a referral card, Mr. Vargas.?\'94\
\
He fumbles in his pocket again and then passes over the card. \'93Yes, you can call me Mickey.\'94\
